<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Dear Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Documents<o:p></o:p></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We have included the documents as requested.&nbsp; <=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">The documents are released to you on the basis that =
it contains personal information that you are entitled to receive under the=
 Privacy Act 2020.&nbsp; Due to the confidential nature of that information=
, Tower requires that you do not disclose
 the information provided to you by Tower&#8217;s staff to any third partie=
s, without Tower&#8217;s prior written consent.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Note that if the personal information held by Tower =
is incorrect, you may request correction of that information.<o:p></o:p></p=
>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">If you have any further questions or concerns, pleas=
e contact us on 0800 808 808.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please use the link below to get access <o:p></o:p><=
/p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><a href=3D"https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sc393b8aa=
6fe64f69b68334ef28b2cb7a">https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sc393b8aa6fe64f69=
b68334ef28b2cb7a</a><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Regards<o:p></o:p></p>
